6 An Act relating to damages; amending 23 O.S. 2021,
Section 61.2, which relates to limitation on
7 noneconomic loss compensation; increasing maximum
limitation on compensation for noneconomic loss;
8 clarifying applicability of provisions; updating
statutory references; and providing an effective
9 date.
